'''英國鐵路800型動車組'''是一款柴油-電力[[雙動力源鐵路車輛|雙動力源鐵路車輛]]。

該款列車屬[[日立製作所|日立]][[A-train|A-train]]系列，由2015年起分別在英格蘭東北部的{{le|牛頓艾克利夫|Newton Aycliffe}}鎮日立分廠，與日本[[山口縣|山口縣]]的笠戶事業所製造<ref name="hket">{{cite news|url=http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1136140|title=日立英國鐵路車廠11月投產|publisher=信報財經新聞|date=2015-09-04|accessdate=2015-10-02|language=zh-hk|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002145122/http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1136140|archivedate=2015-10-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，已從2017年起正式投入服務，主要行走[[東海岸主線|東海岸主線]]及[[大西部主線|大西部主線]]的高速車次<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.gov.uk/government/news/government-gives-green-light-for-more-state-of-the-art-intercity-trains|title=Government gives green light for more state-of-the-art intercity trains|publisher=[[英國運輸部|英國運輸部]]|date=2013-07-18|accessdate=2015-10-02|language=en|archivedate=2019-08-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190823173844/https://www.gov.uk/government/news/government-gives-green-light-for-more-state-of-the-art-intercity-trains|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==背景與設計==
[[File:Azuma_and_HST_at_Leeds_station_(geograph_6187255).jpg|thumb]] 。]]
800型是基於英國政府的城際特快計畫（Intercity Express Programme），用以取代部分行駛於大西部主線與東海岸主線的老舊 [[InterCity_125|InterCity 125]] 列車，[[東海岸主線|東海岸主線]]上的 [[InterCity_225|InterCity 225]] 列車。 

800型可以由架空線經集電弓獲取電力，或是由車架下方的柴油引擎提供電力，大西部主線本來是訂購全電力的801型。他們的本型車是有可能移除柴油引擎而更改成全電力列車的。<ref name="devonliveupdate">{{cite web|title=Great Western Railway gives update on when we will get new express trains|url=https://www.devonlive.com/news/devon-news/great-western-railway-gives-update-1799519|website=devonlive|accessdate=28 September 2018}}</ref>

800型列車雖然可由單人駕駛，但幾乎所有班車上都有一位列車長。大西部鐵路牛津與貝德溫（Bedwyn）區間的列車僅有單人操作而無列車長，駕駛經由駕駛室內的監視器注意車門開閉情形。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/82840/tts-redacted.pdf|title=IEP Trains technical specfication|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref> 有列車長的列車，仍由駕駛控制車門打開，由車長負責關門，駕駛在開車前由車側監視器再次確認車門開閉情形。<ref>"RMT ACCEPTS GWR’S IEP OPERATION PLANS" Modern Railways July 2017 Volume 74 Number 826 page 10</ref>

==動力車==
雖然置於車架下方，仍採V型12汽缸設計的柴油引擎。801型的每編組（5至9節車）僅有一部柴油引擎發電機組，能在外部電力供應失常時提供緊急電力，以有限度地移動列車與供應輔助機械之用。但在800型與802型，5節車編組有3部引擎發電機組（位於第2、3、4車下方），9節車編組有5部引擎發電機組（位於第2、3、5、7、8車）。<ref name="HitachiReview-63-10" />不過車架下方空間有限，影響散熱，引擎發電機組容易過熱，在夏季會影響運行。<ref>{{cite magazine |title=Too Darned Hot |magazine=Modern Railways |date=August 2018 |volume=75 |issue=839 |page=37 }}</ref>
==意外與事故==
* 2019年11月13日，一列倫敦東北鐵路（LNER）的 ''Azuma'' 列車(800109)在里茲的內惟爾山車輛基地，追撞一組43型柴油機車 (43300)。當時兩車行駛時速分別為24公里與8公里，結果800型列車的3節車廂出軌，其第一輛車與43型柴油機車的尾車嚴重受損。調查報告顯示事故主因為司機員操作失誤，次因為訓練不足。而碰撞之所以後果嚴重，也要歸因於800型在設計時未考慮到低於36公里時速的碰撞以及出軌時的影響。<ref>{{Cite web|title=LNER delays after trains crash at Leeds depot|publisher=BBC News Online|date=14 November 2019|access-date=15 November 2019|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-leeds-50425237}}</ref><ref name=RAIBinitial>{{cite web |url=https://www.gov.uk/government/news/train-collision-at-neville-hill |title= Train collision at Neville Hill |publisher=Rail Accident Investigation Branch |access-date=22 November 2019}}</ref><ref name=RAIBNeville>{{cite web |url=https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/935941/R132020_201118_Neville_Hill.pdf |title=Collision and Derailment at Neville Hill 13 November 2019 |publisher=Rail Accidents Investigation Branch |access-date=18 November 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.gov.uk/raib-reports/report-13-2020-collision-and-derailment-at-neville-hill|title=Report 13/2020: Collision and derailment at Neville Hill|website=GOV.UK}}</ref>
*由於轉向架的橫搖阻尼器框架發現裂痕， 2021 年4月26日大西部鐵路暫停8組5輛車編組的800型列車的營運。<ref>{{cite web |title=Fatigue cracks sideline GWR Class 800s |url=https://www.railwaygazette.com/uk/fatigue-cracks-sideline-gwr-class-800s/59012.article |website=Rail Business UK |access-date=8 May 2021}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=High-speed GWR trains withdrawn over crack fears |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-56902528 |website=bbc.co.uk |publisher=BBC |access-date=8 May 2021 |date=27 April 2021 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="MR2021-06yaw">{{cite magazine|last1=Ford |first1=Roger |title=Yaw damper problems hit CAF and Hitachi |magazine=Modern railways |date=June 2021 |pages=28-32}}</ref>
*在2021年5月8日，由於一部維修中的列車發現轉向架承樑焊接處有裂痕，大西部鐵路、倫敦東北鐵路、赫爾鐵路的大部分800型列車暫停營運。<ref name="2021-05-10-bt">{{cite news |last1=McWhirter |first1=Alex |title=UK rail disruption expected to last for some time |url=https://www.businesstraveller.com/business-travel/2021/05/10/uk-rail-disruption-expected-to-last-for-some-time/ |access-date=10 May 2021 |work=Business Traveller |date=10 May 2021}}</ref><ref name="MR2021-06news">{{cite magazine |title=Cracks crisis |magazine=Modern railways |date=June 2021 |pages=6-9}}</ref><ref name="MR2021-07cracks">{{cite magazine|last1=Ford |first1=Roger |title=Rolling stock cracks crisis update |magazine=Modern railways |date=July 2021 |pages=34–35}}</ref> 這可能與大西部鐵路4月26日維修列車時發現的問題相關。<ref>{{cite web |title=Rail chaos: Operators suspend trains over fears of cracks in carriages |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2021/05/08/major-rail-disruption-operators-inspect-trains-crack-fears/ |website=telegraph.co.uk |publisher=The Telegraph |access-date=8 May 2021 |date=8 May 2021}}</ref> 這使得倫敦往蘇格蘭以及英國西部的許多列車取消。<ref name="2021-05-08-bbc">{{cite news |last1=Therrien |first1=Alex |title=High-speed rail services cancelled after cracks found in trains |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-57036247 |access-date=8 May 2021 |work=BBC News |date=8 May 2021}}</ref><ref name="2021-05-08-guardian">{{cite news |last1=Otte |first1=Jedidajah |title=UK high-speed trains cancelled after cracks found in carriages |url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/may/08/uk-high-speed-trains-cancelled-after-cracks-found-in-carriages |access-date=8 May 2021 |work=The Guardian |date=8 May 2021 |language=en}}</ref> 由於維修困難，何時可以解決，據報未能確定。<ref name="2021-05-10-bt" /> 2021年5月13日起有些列車恢復行駛，不過受損較嚴重的列車還需要維修，且所有的列車都需要更徹底的維修以長久解決問題。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Harrison |first1=Emma |title=Trains reintroduced after safety checks prompted by cracks |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-57100278 |work=BBC News |date=13 May 2021}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Industry reveals Intercity Express recovery plan |url=https://www.railnews.co.uk/news/2021/05/13-industry-reveals-intercity-express-recovery.html |work=Railnews |date=13 May 2021}}</ref>

